This paper deals with facial expression transfer, editing, and recognition using a generative adversarial network. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper involves artificial intelligence techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another possible category. The paper also involves multimedia techniques, which makes cs.MM (Multimedia) another possible category. Finally, the paper involves human-computer interaction techniques, which makes cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) another possible category.
